Class OracleVertexQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tinkerpop.blueprints.util.DefaultQuery

        • oracle.pg.common.OracleVertexQuery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.tinkerpop.blueprints.Query, com.tinkerpop.blueprints.VertexQuery

    public class OracleVertexQuery
extends com.tinkerpop.blueprints.util.DefaultVertexQuery
    Oracle implementation of VertexQuery. A VertexQuery object defines a collection of filters and modifiers that are used to intelligently select edges from a vertex.
